                            Scripts for SC/5
                            ================


This directory contains the scripts referred to in SC/5: `The 2-D CCD
Data Reduction Cookbook'.   The scripts use the C-shell and are intended
to be run from the Unix command line.  See SC/5 for further details.

The scripts are:

  changetype.csh - convert to a new data format,
  clipim.csh     - clip an image,
  doapp.csh      - process compressed files using HISTPEAK in ESP,
  dostats.csh    - process compressed files using STATS in KAPPA,
  fitsinfo.csh   - Examine specified FITS keywords,
  saodisp.csh    - automatically scale an image display with SAOIMAGE,
  scaledisp.csh  - automatically scale an image display with DISPLAY in KAPPA.


